{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762173417752","path":null,"data":{"id":2469,"title":"ManuLife:補充「自願醫保附加保障」已生效保單的特別安排","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1701061482835,"tags":["宏利保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;繼 2023 年11月3日 IFP Newsflash 發佈新推出產品<strong><span style=\"color: #337008;\">「宏利晉逸自願醫保附加保障」</span></strong>，現特此補充有關增加自願醫保附加保障於已生效保單的一些特別安排，以符合「醫務衞生局 (醫衞局)」對自願醫保產品的要求。主要安排如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. 根據自願醫保計劃規則，<strong>自願醫保產品必須設有<span style=\"color: #337008;\">冷靜期</span>，並適用於新保單及附加已簽發之保單的客戶</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. 與自願醫保基本計劃一樣，<strong>自願醫保計劃規則亦要求自願醫保附加保障的保單文件需於簽發後 <span style=\"color: #337008;\">9 天內</span>送遞給客戶。</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 流程詳述如下:</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-11-27/6806738853824f67a49f724b261ec1fa.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"IFP Bulletin 510.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-11-27/49ba735b98ed445a8c6b1a14109855cd.pdf","uploadTime":1701050275358,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"MANULIFE","companyName":"宏利保險","productCodes":["MANULIFE:MSLVSBAP","MANULIFE:MSLVSB"],"productNames":["宏利晉逸自願醫保附加保障(精選計劃)","宏利晉逸自願醫保附加保障(智選計劃)"],"companyCodes":["MANULIFE"],"companyNames":["宏利保險"],"startEffectiveDate":null,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}